11. Final Approval Statement

This SOP certifies that the organisation has implemented a fully autonomous AI-controlled industrial environment in which decision-making has been successfully transferred from deterministic systems and accountable humans to a probabilistic entity that generates explanations faster than consequences occur.

The system is therefore considered compliant with the Strategic Innovation Before Understanding Framework (SIBUF) and is approved for immediate deployment, continuous operation, and retrospective risk assessment.

In the event of any negative outcomes, it is formally recorded that:
	•	The AI followed its training,
	•	The humans followed the AI,
	•	Management followed a trend,
	•	And the documentation was fully compliant.

Therefore, no procedure violations have occurred.

